room_title: Escape room "Party Room The Sequel (Simon's Theater)" by Escape Chambers in Des Moines
room_description: Simon says to come over, so you come over. Simon likes puzzles, riddles, and games. The last time you went and visited Simon he had plenty of tricks up his sleeve and you’re sure this time will be no different. Simon’s suggested a “movie night” and while you’re ready for the sequel, who knows what he has in store…
